Creators Kate Elisabeth and Joel M are your hosts for this Creator Close Up. Find out how they both established their brands and evolved their content to take their channels to the next level by experimenting with formats to reach new audiences and building strategies to make multi-format work for them. Get the lowdown on forming new partnerships and creating beyond the platform - this is inspiration all the way.
